episode_summary: In this episode, Brittany Ranew shares her journey from a music background to becoming a top-producing REALTOR in St. Petersburg, Florida. She discusses overcoming mindset challenges, building a personal brand through community engagement, and the importance of meaningful conversations in real estate. Brittany also highlights her use of a podcast to connect with local businesses and offers insights into maintaining a productive morning routine.
